reviewText: Arrived quickly. If you love Adam Sandler, this is a great way to get three of his past favorites.
Reign over me is my favorite movie of all time and the other too are pretty good too
Adam Sandler in some "sappy" movies,  I like Sandler my wife likes "sappy".  Win-win at a good price.
Not Adam Sandler's funniest movies cause these are mostly dramas but I like them.
